    public class TorgScreen
extends com.vaadin.flow.component.html.Div
    TorgScreen -- A generic full screen in TORG design.

    You may use the default methods for handling the center column and have special methods to handle the left and right column if needed.

    Since:
    0.3.0 2021-04-18
